OL,3,CAward-nominated PC barred for sexual
OL,4,Cmisconduct
OL,6,FA police officer who was nominated for
OL,7,Fa bravery award after saving people
OL,8,Ffrom a tower block fire has been
OL,9,Fbarred from policing for sexual
OL,10,Fimpropriety.
OL,12,FFormer Avon and Somerset officer,
OL,13,FJustin Robbie, ran into Twinnell House
OL,14,Fin Easton, Bristol, with no protective
OL,15,Fequipment and saved the lives of two
OL,16,Fmen who had climbed out of a top floor
OL,17,Fwindow.
