OL,3,CAward-nominated PC barred for sexual
OL,4,Cmisconduct
OL,6,FThe hearing found that PC Robbie had
OL,7,Fsent inappropriate requests,
OL,8,Fcommunication, and an unsolicited
OL,9,Fimage to a female colleague.
OL,11,FTemporary Superintendent Sharon Baker,
OL,12,FHead of our Professional Standards
OL,13,FDepartment, said: "PC Robbie's conduct
OL,14,Ffell well below the standards required
OL,15,Fof anyone serving in the police.
OL,17,F"He behaved in a manner that
OL,18,Fdiscredits the police service and will
OL,19,Fno doubt undermine public confidence.
