OL,3,CAward-nominated PC barred for sexual
OL,4,Cmisconduct
OL,6,FShe added: "There can be no place in
OL,7,Fpolicing for anyone acting in such an
OL,8,Finappropriate way. His actions towards
OL,9,Fthe woman violated her dignity, who he
OL,10,Fknew did not want him to behave in
OL,11,Fsuch a manner.
OL,13,F"We hope this decision to bar him from
OL,14,Fworking within policing ever again
OL,15,Fsends a strong message to the public
OL,16,Fthat such behaviour will not be
OL,17,Ftolerated whatsoever."
