OL,3,CAward-nominated PC barred for sexual
OL,4,Cmisconduct
OL,6,FThe former police officer was found to
OL,7,Fhave breached four professional
OL,8,Fstandards after a two-day hearing at
OL,9,Fthe force's headquarters in Portishead.
OL,11,FFormer PC Justin Robbie was one of the
OL,12,Ffirst responders on the scene of a
OL,13,Ffatal fire at Twinnell House in Easton
OL,14,Fin September 2022.
OL,16,FIn 2023, he was recognised at the
OL,17,FNational Police Bravery Awards for his
OL,18,Factions when he ran into the burning
OL,19,FEaston tower block and directed
OL,20,Fresidents to safety.
